<li>Contact Drill</li>
<li>Immediate Ambush Drill</li>
<li>Counter Ambush Drill</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Hull-down" title="Hull-down">Hull-down</a> (in <a href="/wiki/Armoured_warfare" title="Armoured warfare">armoured warfare</a>)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Shoot-and-scoot" title="Shoot-and-scoot">Shoot-and-scoot</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Fire_and_Movement" title="Fire and Movement">Fire and Movement</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Four_Fs_(military)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Four Fs (military) (page does not exist)">Four Fs</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Overwatch" title="Overwatch">Overwatch</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bounding_Overwatch" title="Bounding Overwatch" class="mw-redirect">Bounding Overwatch</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
