</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Patrolling" title="Patrolling">Patrolling</a>
<ul>
<li>Reconnaissance Patrol</li>
<li>Fighting Patrol</li>
<li>Standing Patrol (OP/LP)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Saturation_patrol" title="Saturation patrol">Saturation patrol</a></li>
